    "description": "<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320890/extras/95e3dd89157f3aedaa974879c28c0e9c.poster.avif?t=1742659215\" width=672 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320890/extras/95e3dd89157f3aedaa974879c28c0e9c.webm?t=1742659215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320890/extras/95e3dd89157f3aedaa974879c28c0e9c.mp4?t=1742659215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《午夜迪斯科》是一款快节奏的自上而下的双摇杆射击类游戏，你必须在被丑陋的外星眼球怪物侵占的舞池中生存。<br><br>消灭大量的跨维度入侵者。收集黑胶唱片以升级一个极其深入的技能树，解锁改变游戏的特权和能力。打开宝箱获得强力物品，为每次紧张刺激的短程跑动做好准备。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320890/extras/e016beed9bc142eb7327d903ee6df50b.poster.avif?t=1742659215\" width=672 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320890/extras/e016beed9bc142eb7327d903ee6df50b.webm?t=1742659215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320890/extras/e016beed9bc142eb7327d903ee6df50b.mp4?t=1742659215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>超过20种独特的敌人类型，每种都有独特的攻击模式，将不懈地追捕你。幸运的是，你可以通过混合和匹配大量的升级、增强和随机修改器来创建截然不同的构建 - 确保每次运行都不一样。<br><br>哦，小心脚下……有便便。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320890/extras/25e34edb2be54646c08780086effdc08.poster.avif?t=1742659215\" width=360 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320890/extras/25e34edb2be54646c08780086effdc08.webm?t=1742659215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320890/extras/25e34edb2be54646c08780086effdc08.mp4?t=1742659215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>特点：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 大量的构建种类，保证无限的重玩性<br></li><li> 短时间的Roguelike跑动，非常适合即玩即停<br></li><li> 在线排行榜<br></li><li> 紧张刺激的快节奏游戏玩法<br></li><li> 大量的敌人群体，具有独特和具有挑战性的行为</li></ul>",
